One of the oldest and famous dargha mosque  of Arcot famously known as Tajpura mosque.
Situated in Tajpura village which is named after this famous darga.
Very old and calm place with very old trees and green gardens .
A very good place for peaceful meditation.
Silent atmosphere in mosque premises gives very good feel.
Sufi concepts can be learned here.
Mentally disturbed people can visit this place for their good vibes.
